Most recent data refers to the data with the latest date for each stock.; 
User engagement metrics include the count of accesses and total duration.; 
Stock performance data includes closing prices and volumes.; 
The query assumes that the most recent data is the most relevant for analysis.

- A daily report is a report generated every day; 
- A published status means the report is publicly available; 
- Stock exchanges are platforms where stocks are bought and sold.
